sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Owner as Evaluation owner
    participant Bench as Benchmark context
    participant Run as Automated benchmark
    participant Challenge as TEVV or red-team challenge
    participant Report as Evaluation report
    participant Review as Reviewer decision
    participant Claim as Bounded claim ledger
    Owner->>Bench: Define the claim being tested and excluded claims
    Bench->>Run: Bind dataset, task, metric, and reproducibility context
    Run->>Challenge: Submit run evidence plus validity limits
    Challenge->>Report: Add challenge scope, failures, and uncertainty
    Report->>Review: Present caveats, provenance, and release request
    Review->>Claim: Approve only bounded source-backed wording
    Review-->>Bench: Otherwise revise, retest, or add caveat
